TITLE: Composite Password/Anonymous Authentication Flow Sequence Diagram
DESCRIPTION: Mermaid sequence diagram showing the authentication flow for a composite plugin that provides both password-based and anonymous authentication options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/deephaven/web-client-ui/blob/main/packages/auth-plugins/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: mermaid
CODE:
```
sequenceDiagram
  participant W as Web UI
  participant CP as CompositePlugin
  participant AP as AnonymousPlugin
  participant PP as PasswordPlugin
  participant J as JS API
  W->>CP: Login
  CP->>CP: Prompt for authentication method
  activate CP
    alt Password login
      activate PP
        loop Until success
          PP->>PP: Show Login UI
          PP->>J: client.login(password)
          alt Login success
            J-->>PP: Login success
          else Login failure
            J-->>PP: Login failure
            PP->>PP: Show login error
          end
        end
        PP-->>CP: Login success
      deactivate PP
    else Anonymous login
      activate AP
        AP->>J: client.login(anonymous)
        J-->>AP: Login success
        AP-->>CP: Login success
      deactivate AP
    end
    CP-->>W: Login success
  deactivate CP
```

